title: Seamus Haji @ MN2S  #79
text:
This seasons opening of Milk n 2 Sugars in Ibiza was full (with girls!) as Seamus Haji took control of the decks. He quickly proceeded to drop funk bombs on the dance floor, including several of his own productions and remixes.
